Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.26,0:02:48.09,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,騙人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.27,0:02:50.46,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你這個被稱為「鬼神」的安藤前輩會…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.12,0:02:52.20,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,難以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.47,0:02:53.80,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,血塗蝶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.15,0:02:57.43,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 血塗蝶什麼的倒是第一次聽說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.63,0:03:00.40,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,血塗蝶 是其他地盤上的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.80,0:03:04.40,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,血塗蝶 跟蝴蝶刀有什麼關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.54,0:03:06.05,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,住嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.26,0:03:08.49,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別一直反覆說這名字了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.66,0:03:11.75,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,血塗蝶 不過是網遊的玩家名而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.82,0:03:14.40,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在現實中被這麼認真地叫…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.77,0:03:16.64,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太羞恥了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.03,0:03:19.80,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你們 別擅自去查探她的底細
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.29,0:03:24.07,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,血塗蝶…可是活在黑暗世界的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.94,0:03:27.15,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我啊 已經意識到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.52,0:03:29.10,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,跟血塗蝶對話時
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.58,0:03:32.19,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,發現我們做的事情就跟過家家一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.95,0:03:35.45,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說實話被震撼到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.90,0:03:39.99,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這世上…竟然有像血塗蝶這樣的女人存在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.98,0:03:43.49,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,憑那樣的身軀背負著這個國家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.92,0:03:48.12,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她可是…在跟外頭的暴力集團對幹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.35,0:03:52.79,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能被安藤前輩這麼評價的人…竟然存在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.31,0:03:56.06,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我怎麼都沒法認同
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.28,0:03:58.95,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,請讓我親眼見見血塗蝶！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.05,0:04:01.69,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這蠢貨 你不相信我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.98,0:04:04.80,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,事情鬧得越來越大
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.29,0:04:07.58,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣下去 我會沒法在街上走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.98,0:04:10.88,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我…相信安藤前輩的實力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.59,0:04:14.67,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,正因如此 即使要把血塗蝶拖出來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.21,0:04:15.81,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,算我一個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.33,0:04:18.76,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她絕對用了什麼卑鄙的手段
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.25,0:04:21.76,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不然…安藤前輩怎麼會輸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.12,0:04:22.60,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,憑我們自己
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.07,0:04:25.43,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,憑我們自己的雙手 一定要找出來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.69,0:04:28.15,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是時候抓血塗蝶了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.68,0:04:31.44,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,安藤…前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.73,0:04:33.13,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.16,0:04:33.78,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別動！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.67,0:04:37.60,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別說任何話 絕對…別回頭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.24,0:04:46.09,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,從…從哪裡出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.15,0:04:48.80,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,血塗蝶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.38,0:04:51.95,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這…這就是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.49,0:04:55.89,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,血塗蝶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.62,0:05:01.66,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 這就是…血塗蝶？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.93,0:05:05.00,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好像…跟想像中的不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.66,0:05:07.91,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還以為會更加接近女突擊隊員的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.97,0:05:13.72,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,多虧安藤狠狠地捧我上天 成功讓他們都洩氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.29,0:05:16.60,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣應該比較好說話了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.97,0:05:20.55,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有…什麼事 血塗蝶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.43,0:05:25.18,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我找你有話要說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.63,0:05:28.78,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我想我倆單獨聊一聊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.80,0:05:35.80,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你們別動
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.22,0:05:38.25,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我會馬上回來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.38,0:05:40.16,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,安藤前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.48,0:05:41.27,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,給我在那等著
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.44,0:05:45.74,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 有話說是指什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.85,0:05:48.58,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我會按約離隊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.88,0:05:49.99,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.94,0:05:54.38,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,難道…你是想拉我進黑社會
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.58,0:05:55.89,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對 沒錯！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.72,0:05:58.80,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你太高估我了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.18,0:06:03.35,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒有舉過槍桿 也沒有殺人的心理準備
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.18,0:06:03.63,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}沒錯沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.83,0:06:06.00,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,更別說要背負國家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.49,0:06:09.46,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}對 關於這個的事情 全都是誤會
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.55,0:06:16.09,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,確實會有這種反應
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.33,0:06:17.69,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.75,0:06:19.95,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這種黑暗組織之類的東西都不存在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.15,0:06:23.95,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是普通的女高中生 中下等的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.18,0:06:27.63,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不是在開玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.95,0:06:31.69,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說到底 那個 我的腳碰到了排氣管
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.78,0:06:34.06,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我說那個大叔是廢人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.23,0:06:36.49,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,其實是完全沉迷於遊戲裡的人的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.06,0:06:42.55,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沮喪中…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.18,0:06:46.23,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 好在他能比較聽得懂我說的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.41,0:06:48.16,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說到底之前能夠過去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.32,0:06:51.18,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也是因為這人是會傾聽別人的類型
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.63,0:06:53.83,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 我確認一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.00,0:06:54.43,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.60,0:06:57.26,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說 你只是一個普通人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.75,0:07:01.32,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只是路過但不幸地被混混給纏上了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.92,0:07:06.49,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只靠使勁吹牛 完全騙過了那個混混
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.06,0:07:10.26,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,讓他害怕並讓他退出暴走族
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.95,0:07:14.78,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然後被騙的混混 跟傻瓜一樣地
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.95,0:07:16.90,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把吹的牛都告訴給了同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.46,0:07:22.63,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所謂淪為小丑 就是這麼一回事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.26,0:07:25.46,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了 肯定會來頭槌了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.87,0:07:26.80,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,躲不開
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.95,0:07:30.20,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,反而太厲害了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.00,0:07:37.89,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 太了不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.47,0:07:41.52,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 會被他們聽到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.99,0:07:43.00,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.07,0:07:46.26,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,難怪我會有「原來跟外表一樣是普通的女高中生」的反應
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.09,0:07:53.60,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怪不得啊 我就覺得血塗蝶這名字太土了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.03,0:07:58.40,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,血塗蝶 直到剛才我還一臉認真地說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.87,0:08:00.63,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,血塗蝶…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.87,0:08:06.23,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都說了 我不想讓這事張揚出去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.24,0:08:07.58,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明白的明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.95,0:08:11.89,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 對隊伍多多少少的不捨也完全消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.58,0:08:14.63,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,完全是你的勝利了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.02,0:08:19.33,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我也會把小丑演到最後的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.01,0:08:21.46,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.95,0:08:26.06,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的 你只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.58,0:08:29.69,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,安藤前輩 好慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.39,0:08:33.03,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的 根本不需要擔心他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.03,0:08:37.18,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,安藤前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.62,0:08:39.89,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙 血塗蝶她
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.19,0:08:42.46,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太危險了 太強了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.53,0:08:44.55,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到底發生了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.92,0:08:49.55,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,來了 這樣下去大家都會被幹掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.91,0:08:51.78,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙是怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.09,0:08:54.63,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,慢慢地走 慢慢地走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.35,0:08:56.43,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,毫髮無傷就…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.58,0:08:58.26,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把安藤前輩打到奄奄一息
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.95,0:09:00.23,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看來實力是真的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.44,0:09:01.58,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是蝴蝶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.85,0:09:02.98,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要來了 她的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.24,0:09:06.78,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼她會被稱為血塗蝶的…某個…必殺的招式
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.15,0:09:10.21,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,方圓一公里內的人 不知道為什麼會死掉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.71,0:09:14.18,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你們 快跑！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.75,0:09:18.03,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,聽好了 給我忘掉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.25,0:09:20.12,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別再提這個名字了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.66,0:09:22.18,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對別再扯上關係了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.67,0:09:23.95,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你也快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.08,0:09:25.26,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.52,0:09:27.70,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我要打敗血塗蝶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.32,0:09:30.78,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只要是為了安藤前輩 我就算丟了這條性命…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.78,0:09:33.09,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我說了逃跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.51,0:09:34.66,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,殺了你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.97,0:09:46.48,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多就這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.04,0:09:49.03,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嚇唬到那種程度 應該沒問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.58,0:09:50.22,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.65,0:09:54.18,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,丟下摩托的傢伙未來可沒有資格當暴走族的老大
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.69,0:09:57.03,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.33,0:10:01.63,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,請用這個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.89,0:10:10.75,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果保管了這種東西 事情又會變得很麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.17,0:10:13.15,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再見了 血塗蝶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.17,0:10:16.35,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都說了 別提那個名字了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.30,0:10:24.18,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,話說 前陣子不是有個人跟暴走族一起騎摩托上學嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.92,0:10:26.69,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然後呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.15,0:10:30.00,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有 那個帶著暴走族的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.04,0:10:33.75,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好像自稱是血什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.06,0:10:36.44,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,總感覺在哪聽過
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.15,0:10:39.46,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,以前沉迷遊戲的時候？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.86,0:10:43.12,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 畢竟當時用這名字一起玩過
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.63,0:10:44.92,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千緒 你知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.71,0:10:47.29,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不太清楚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.11,0:10:51.72,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來得幹掉這傢伙了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.04,0:10:54.97,qianxu-cut,NTP,0,0,0,,{\shad0\fad(1500,0)\fs120\c&H601FB2&\3c&HFFFEFD&\pos(958,884)}千緒的{\fs150}通學路
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.34,0:10:59.13,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(300,0)}Bloody Butterfly
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.96,0:10:59.15,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被說土了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.14,0:11:02.26,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那那個人的隊名是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.13,0:11:02.54,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs60\fad(300,0)\bord1\fn@方正小标宋_GBK\frz270.8\b0\c&H424242&\pos(978,306)}我記得名字是安藤…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.64,0:11:02.54,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs60\fad(300,0)\bord1\fn@方正小标宋_GBK\frz270.8\b0\c&H424242&\pos(1672,522)}會出來嗎…
Dialogue: 1,0:11:03.02,0:11:03.42,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是這個了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.55,0:11:04.47,qianxu-huamian3,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord1\fs70\c&H52555A&\b1\3c&H5C5857&\pos(1010,650)}不知道為何星空會的安藤離隊了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.55,0:11:04.47,qianxu-huamian3,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs70\c&H52555A&\b1\3c&H5C5857&\move(960,968,946,1042,500,0)}真的假的星空會完了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.46,0:11:06.86,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然是非混混名字
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.99,0:11:09.00,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 有點可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.65,0:11:14.90,qianxu-title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(900,700)\bord0.1\shad8\blur6\pos(1499.2,899.6)\4c&H6E61CD&}卡巴迪4人組
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.65,0:11:12.32,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs50}註：卡巴迪是一種運動項目，起源於印度。運動場地為矩形，由一條中線橫向分割成兩個半場。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.65,0:11:12.32,qianxu-zhengwen,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs50}兩隊場上各有7名隊員，場下5名替補，各占一個半場，並各派一名「進攻者」衝到對方半場，
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.65,0:11:12.32,qianxu-zhengwen,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs50}儘可能「觸殺」對方隊員，並回到自己半場。觸殺數即得分數。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.65,0:11:12.32,qianxu-zhengwen,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs50}但如果被「攔截」而沒有回到半場，則不得分。相反「攔截」成功一方得1分。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.00,0:11:15.52,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真奈菜 能把手伸到這邊來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.95,0:11:17.66,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.28,0:11:21.91,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,難得我用了一晚練習了CQC
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.28,0:11:21.91,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs50}註：CQC指Close Quarters Combat，即近身格鬥術。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.55,0:11:25.06,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼 又是受遊戲的影響？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.23,0:11:27.38,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過如果伸了手會變得怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.60,0:11:32.00,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,動作好帥 電影反覆看了很多遍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.86,0:11:35.70,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你真是過著桑葚色的青春
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.86,0:11:35.70,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs50}註：日本有關於「土留め色」的說法。一說是指桑葚色。桑葚即桑樹果實。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.86,0:11:35.70,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs50}桑葚色在日本部分文化中具有「病態的」「不明確」的印象。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.48,0:11:37.25,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣來了就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.80,0:11:38.73,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣來了就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.10,0:11:39.95,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣來了就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.16,0:11:41.15,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被抓住了就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.23,0:11:42.38,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼 盂蘭盆舞？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.45,0:11:44.46,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,高一的女生在做什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.00,0:11:48.89,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣 然後這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.03,0:11:54.64,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 快點告訴我你電腦視頻文件夾的密碼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.79,0:11:56.00,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,唯…唯獨那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.47,0:11:57.78,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,殺了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.25,0:12:02.80,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過說起來千緒你運動神經好得有點浪費了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.75,0:12:05.89,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來明天有體測
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.12,0:12:07.75,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千緒今年要怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.20,0:12:09.57,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今年也隨便來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.19,0:12:15.15,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千緒你好歹是運動部的 難得能運動就拿出真本事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.31,0:12:16.23,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.32,0:12:20.95,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,顯眼一次的話 之後體育祭和球技大賽不就會一直被期待嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.38,0:12:24.23,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我明明只是想靜悄悄地度日
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.80,0:12:27.03,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,出現了 是千緒的中下論
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.49,0:12:30.75,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個國家連一次的失敗都不被允許
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.03,0:12:33.49,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,首先 關於「體測常有的事」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.58,0:12:37.46,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,反覆橫跳的動作不是很搞笑嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.82,0:12:42.55,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不 「體測常有的事」這個詞本身就已經很新鮮了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.20,0:12:46.69,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,全力左往右往 有點像奇怪的舞蹈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.28,0:12:48.69,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千緒 用全力…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.86,0:12:50.80,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣 你看 你懂不
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.88,0:12:52.92,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千緒千緒 說下「卡巴迪」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.98,0:12:55.53,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,卡巴迪卡巴迪卡巴迪…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.42,0:12:58.98,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和卡巴迪太適合了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.09,0:13:00.60,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,連表情也很像
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.68,0:13:01.98,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很累的你知不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.14,0:13:03.95,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我都不知道卡巴迪的規則
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.12,0:13:05.60,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千緒告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.79,0:13:07.26,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.40,0:13:08.26,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.26,0:13:09.75,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一大早就很精神呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.40,0:13:11.83,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,正好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.89,0:13:12.67,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.22,0:13:14.32,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這位前輩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.73,0:13:15.20,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.87,0:13:17.55,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鮫島學園三年級
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.86,0:13:19.20,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,卡巴迪部部長
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.76,0:13:20.99,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,久志取圓
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.66,0:13:23.43,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 卡巴迪…部？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.32,0:13:26.23,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,搞砸了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.57,0:13:29.58,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你們剛剛說了「告訴我卡巴迪的規則」對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.77,0:13:32.18,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也聽到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.58,0:13:35.18,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不 那個 抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.28,0:13:38.72,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 沒事哦 我知道你們沒惡意的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.87,0:13:39.46,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.71,0:13:42.03,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只是對卡巴迪有興趣而已對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.10,0:13:43.52,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 啊 是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.89,0:13:46.20,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想知道卡巴迪的規則是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.41,0:13:48.16,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.72,0:13:51.38,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好 那我就來教你們
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.17,0:13:53.49,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,去裡面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.80,0:13:55.20,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.80,0:13:57.64,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好像變成好麻煩的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.56,0:14:01.53,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,卡巴迪卡巴迪卡巴迪…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.72,0:14:05.40,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就像這樣進攻的一方在敵陣的時候要一直說卡巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.47,0:14:09.00,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的一直在說卡巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.35,0:14:10.78,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然後在憋不住氣之前
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.00,0:14:13.89,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,觸碰對手 回到自己的陣地
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.00,0:14:15.78,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,觸碰到的人數就是分數
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.01,0:14:18.45,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被觸碰到的對象要到場外去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.91,0:14:20.23,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.46,0:14:22.55,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,進攻方交替出一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.75,0:14:24.66,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然後對方隊伍則要躲開
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.78,0:14:26.66,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就和抓人遊戲差不多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.83,0:14:27.23,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.63,0:14:29.43,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哇怎麼樣都無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.24,0:14:33.23,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然真的在上學路上開始了卡巴迪講座
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.60,0:14:35.35,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上就是上課時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.63,0:14:37.63,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我想早點解放啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.03,0:14:39.89,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要說和抓人遊戲不一樣的點的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.06,0:14:42.03,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是守備一方也有得分的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.41,0:14:45.14,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這樣把扮鬼的人抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.52,0:14:48.69,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,讓其完全無法行動的話 就是守備一方得分
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.20,0:14:51.86,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,進攻一方是碰 守備一方是抓
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.97,0:14:53.15,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,用一句話總結就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.26,0:14:54.75,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,簡單就是好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.78,0:14:55.78,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,受教了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.89,0:14:58.20,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好 那來模擬戰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.69,0:15:00.52,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你們要是輸了就要入部
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.98,0:15:06.75,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要是我隱退了卡巴迪部也就人數不夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.05,0:15:10.26,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到居然會有對卡巴迪有興趣的一年級生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.32,0:15:11.66,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.72,0:15:12.95,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.26,0:15:20.72,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 你們不是在一邊玩一邊小看卡巴迪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.02,0:15:24.69,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此 我還在想她怎麼說明得這麼細心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.69,0:15:25.86,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原來目的是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.06,0:15:29.95,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊還有點內疚 那邊又是三年級
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.32,0:15:32.20,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想要拒絕是有點困難
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.89,0:15:34.18,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只能上了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.66,0:15:36.32,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那 你們是進攻方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.72,0:15:38.06,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好 上 真奈菜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.12,0:15:39.18,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.32,0:15:40.43,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,按座位號來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.53,0:15:45.34,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,卡巴…卡…卡巴迪卡巴迪卡巴迪…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.69,0:15:47.23,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只是要觸碰對方然後回來對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.41,0:15:54.06,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要亂鬧不要亂鬧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.32,0:15:57.26,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和剛剛的說明完全不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.43,0:16:00.80,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被完全拘束之前也是能逃走的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.80,0:16:02.40,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經動不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.52,0:16:03.95,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,超級認真
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.55,0:16:06.46,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真奈菜出場
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.56,0:16:05.95,qianxu-huamian2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\frz269.4\pos(778,280)}{\fn@微软雅黑\c&H303030&\b0}真奈菜被罰下場
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.63,0:16:08.32,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個我想確認下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.44,0:16:09.82,qianxu-huamian2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\fs60\frz269.6)\move(884,-130,1220,246,790,0)}{\fn@微软雅黑\b0\c&H2D2D2D&}被罰下場就要在場外
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.98,0:16:10.89,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎麼樣才會分出勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.26,0:16:12.69,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,本來是有時間限制的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.86,0:16:15.46,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,讓場外的選手復活的時機也是有的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.66,0:16:18.32,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過已經快上課了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.59,0:16:21.86,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就哪邊隊伍全滅了就算分出勝負好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.18,0:16:25.83,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 那就是下次我出場就輸了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.09,0:16:27.89,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那我是進攻方哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.28,0:16:34.43,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}卡巴迪卡巴迪卡巴迪…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.60,0:16:31.83,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說被細川同學觸碰到並讓她回去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.24,0:16:34.29,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那一瞬間我就會進卡巴迪部
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.78,0:16:37.60,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可是就算我想抓住細川同學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.95,0:16:40.52,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果笨拙地去抓她反而會被當做被觸碰到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.96,0:16:44.49,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 卡巴迪比想像中還要深奧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.46,0:16:46.92,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,反過來想下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.58,0:16:49.78,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果放棄網球部去卡巴迪部的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.92,0:16:52.63,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也有可能在學校會更容易度日
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.26,0:16:55.43,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,初次見面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.57,0:16:57.49,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,新的班級真新鮮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.70,0:16:59.80,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,三谷裳同學你社團加的什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.42,0:17:01.69,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,卡巴迪部哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.43,0:17:03.00,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,河馬？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.13,0:17:03.93,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs50}註：kaba與日語河馬發音相同
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.06,0:17:03.63,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,D？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.35,0:17:05.23,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,卡巴迪卡巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.23,0:17:06.17,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,之後是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.38,0:17:07.26,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,擒抱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.40,0:17:10.17,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.18,0:17:11.83,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要小看卡巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.18,0:17:14.58,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且擒抱的應該是防守者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.75,0:17:17.06,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喊唱著的你應該是進攻者才對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.15,0:17:18.12,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,三谷裳同學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.63,0:17:19.35,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.70,0:17:22.60,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 和我太不適合了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.66,0:17:25.15,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個人 動作很好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.23,0:17:27.29,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,憋不住氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.52,0:17:29.67,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,算是擺脫了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.92,0:17:31.75,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來是輪到我進攻了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.52,0:17:34.72,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對於體力性的長期戰期望不高
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.16,0:17:37.72,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只能這次讓兩個人都出場
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.72,0:17:39.16,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.33,0:17:44.03,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為是謎之古怪的運動我才無法認真起來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.86,0:17:45.95,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,賭上性命的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.08,0:17:48.54,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,遊戲腦 發動
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.05,0:17:53.26,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把卡巴迪的謎之規則 替換成電視遊戲那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.95,0:17:57.49,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對 我是能把觸碰到的東西變成炸彈的能力者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.98,0:18:01.92,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,任務是把那兩個人變成炸彈然後回到安全圈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.18,0:18:04.73,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}再不快點的話就違反規則了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.18,0:18:04.63,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果被抓住的話就會被拷問至死
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.74,0:18:08.75,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,發動這個能力的話需要咒文
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.45,0:18:10.22,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,卡巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.86,0:18:12.18,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好 能接受
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.49,0:18:16.48,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}卡巴迪卡巴迪卡巴迪…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.64,0:18:15.55,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪 注意點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.65,0:18:18.52,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個人 氣氛變了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.60,0:18:20.43,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,卡巴迪卡巴迪卡巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.92,0:18:25.46,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不 雖然有氣勢不過始終還是外行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.79,0:18:26.55,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,追得太深
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.00,0:18:29.12,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在這敵陣的深處就算能觸碰到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.18,0:18:31.69,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也無法從我和小雪的動作中逃脫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.43,0:18:33.30,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到背後了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.86,0:18:34.93,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有空隙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.35,0:18:36.69,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪擒抱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.80,0:18:37.61,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.49,0:18:39.98,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被抓住的話就 這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.03,0:18:42.80,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在她中心移動的瞬間摧毀她
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.75,0:18:45.63,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對不會放手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.78,0:18:49.58,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,細川同學和性格一樣直勾勾地過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.30,0:18:52.19,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,卡巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.83,0:18:55.00,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要讓這雙手放開的話要 這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.78,0:19:08.83,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…久志取前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.08,0:19:09.57,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.58,0:19:12.20,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.43,0:19:13.66,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,三谷裳同學要逃走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.58,0:19:16.60,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,久志取前輩 手手手…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.95,0:19:21.80,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,任務完成
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.87,0:19:26.38,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,觸碰兩個人然後歸來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.82,0:19:28.95,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是我贏了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.19,0:19:31.92,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼會想出這個作戰…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.04,0:19:33.58,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,前輩 那個那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.98,0:19:37.55,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最開始前輩你抓住真奈菜的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.81,0:19:40.20,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看到那個時候的表情我就想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.58,0:19:42.60,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,噫 這個人喜歡妹子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.75,0:19:46.63,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再加上 細川同學進攻的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.74,0:19:50.55,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你看著細川同學擺動著的裙子裡面一直傻笑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.40,0:19:54.20,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以把你抓著我的手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.40,0:19:56.22,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誘導到細川同學的會陰的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.54,0:19:58.18,shitang-huamian,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs50\fad(500,200)\c&HD5D3D3&\pos(1052,962)\3c&HE2DEDF&}OO和XX的中間
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.65,0:19:59.49,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你就會優先能觸摸細川同學的會陰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.71,0:20:01.60,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然後一定會鬆開手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.29,0:20:03.38,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我能斷言
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.69,0:20:07.46,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你比起卡巴迪 更喜歡和女孩子扭在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.62,0:20:10.71,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你在說什麼 我愛著卡巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.16,0:20:13.38,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能動搖我的內心讓我放下卡巴迪的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.47,0:20:14.66,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是不存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.18,0:20:18.83,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那把你的手放下 再打一戰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.36,0:20:33.08,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.78,0:20:37.49,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你還以為今後的人生我還能再摸幾次小雪的會陰？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.80,0:20:39.66,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,身體 無法動彈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.72,0:20:41.69,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那裡是屁股屁股屁股
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.70,0:20:43.46,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是我…輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.99,0:20:49.00,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,請鬆手！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.03,0:20:55.23,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這次 我反省了沒有作為一名卡巴迪選手的覺悟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.63,0:20:58.55,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 那個 很多事都抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.72,0:20:59.72,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不不
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.95,0:21:01.83,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 久志取前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.03,0:21:03.49,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以問一個問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.66,0:21:04.15,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.77,0:21:07.09,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣咪咪才能變成這麼大
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.00,0:21:11.43,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙 真虧她能在這種氣氛下問出這種話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.78,0:21:12.98,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是有病吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.42,0:21:15.80,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不 說起來才注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.06,0:21:18.70,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,回想起來 開始卡巴迪之前
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.86,0:21:21.43,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我還是普通的體型
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.38,0:21:23.49,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到底發生了什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.47,0:21:27.60,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,卡巴迪是發祥於印度的競技
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.90,0:21:31.38,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也有人說其動作中有瑜伽的要素
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.06,0:21:37.23,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說不定就是這瑜伽的要素影響了我的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.78,0:21:45.46,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,卡巴迪卡巴迪卡巴迪…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.53,0:21:48.46,qianxu-cut,NTP,0,0,0,,{\shad0\fad(1500,0)\fs120\pos(958,884)\c&H4CD63C&\3c&HFFFEFF&}千緒的{\fs150\c&H4BD63C&}通學路
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.08,0:21:53.55,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要更加 更加精進卡巴迪才行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.40,0:21:55.03,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.86,0:21:57.22,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪的屁股
Comment: 0,0:00:00.98,0:00:00.98,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,----ed----
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.43,0:23:33.23,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下回的千緒的通學路是由
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.30,0:23:35.94,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「smoke on the sailor」「取到櫻花」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.11,0:23:38.75,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和「真奈菜的通學路」三部分組成
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.83,0:23:39.78,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,敬請期待
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.96,0:23:40.60,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,卡巴迪
